Package: piptm
Type: Package
Title: Computation Engine for the PIP Table Maker
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", email = "your@email.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides the computation engine for the PIP Table Maker system. 
    The package loads survey microdata stored as partitioned Arrow/Parquet datasets 
    and computes poverty, welfare, and inequality measures such as poverty 
    headcount, poverty gap, Gini coefficient, and welfare distribution statistics. 
    The package uses a release manifest system to ensure reproducibility by 
    restricting computations to surveys included in a specific PIP release.
